  "texts": [
    "Mentoring request is initiated from any chat session.",
    "The request is then forwarded to available mentors registered in the system.",
    "Once a mentor accepts the student's request, a new session is created by the session manager, in which the mentor, the student, and the chatbot are members, see Figure 2 and Figure 3.The mentor and student can chat together directly.",
    "At the same time, they can ask questions to the chatbot in that session, using the unique identifier (@) in the question, which triggers the chatbot to read that question, call a limited number of previous interactions between the mentor and the student in the chat before the question to use it as contextual information, and then generate an answer.",
    "Figure 2 shows the chatbot interface for the tasks of user interaction, mentoring request, and user-mentor chat with the chatbot support."
  ],
